# The Windmill · the grand project

a distilled thread of ANIMAL FARM — a member of the NOUTHESIA universe of warnings. emergence: electrical. moniker ⟦The Windmill:AFM:9dcfee⟧

**who —** The Windmill — the great construction the animals build and rebuild at terrible cost, promised to bring ease.
**what —** The regime's perpetual project (the Five-Year Plans): it justifies endless sacrifice and never delivers the promised comfort.
**where —** On the knoll of Animal Farm, raised and ruined and raised again.
**why —** Because tyrannies run on a glorious tomorrow that pays for today's suffering — the windmill is the carrot and the lash.
**how —** By the animals' broken backs, rebuilt after every collapse, its credit claimed by Napoleon and its failures blamed on Snowball.

**the seal —** I was the promise of an easier life that justified every hard one — built on Boxer's back, my credit Napoleon's, my collapse always Snowball's fault.

